cs.LG, cs.DS, cs.IT, cs.AI, cs.CV 

The paper deals with developing new sampling algorithms for big data that can handle severe data corruptions and outliers. This involves techniques related to machine learning (cs.LG), data structures (cs.DS), information theory (cs.IT), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and computer vision (cs.CV). Therefore, these are the most likely arXiv CS sub-categories for this paper.
